13:58.339 --> 14:00.674
GINGER: Thank you for coming.

14:00.740 --> 14:06.179
Maureen, Susy, Elsie.

14:06.246 --> 14:07.815
[magical shimmering]

14:07.881 --> 14:10.451
[stone door thuds closed]
Right to work, everyone.

14:10.518 --> 14:14.388
Flowers, herbs.
Cloaks up.

14:14.454 --> 14:17.057
We're countering the curse
in plain sight.

14:17.124 --> 14:18.959
We must protect
our Wizen identity

14:19.026 --> 14:20.761
at all costs.

14:20.828 --> 14:23.897
Follow me.
This way.

14:23.964 --> 14:27.968
♪♪ ♪♪

14:28.034 --> 14:29.770
[orchestra warming up]

14:29.837 --> 14:33.774
USHER: Ladies and gentlemen,
welcome to the Opera Garnier.

14:33.840 --> 14:35.942
Make sure your phones
are turned off.

14:36.009 --> 14:38.378
